return ['messages'=>['/high-jewellery/'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6/','<p><span style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; text-align: start;">Clouds have always held a sentimental value in Chinese literature. Yun Cai looks to the popular verses by acclaimed poets Li Bai and Xu Zhimo for inspiration.</span></p>'=>'<p><span style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; text-align: start;">雲在中國文學中具有情感價值。〈雲彩〉從著名詩人李白和徐志摩的經典詩句裡，尋找靈感。 </span></p>','<p>A lariat-style necklace inspired by the hand fan in a folded position. Made from 18k rose gold and 2.34 carat round diamonds in total.</p>'=>'<p>靈感來自折疊扇的流蘇式項鍊。由18K玫瑰金製成，鑲嵌總重量2.34克拉的圓形鑽石，演繹新舊融合之美。 </p>','<p>An enamel foldable hand fan crafted from 18k rose gold, featuring a cloud print adorned with round diamonds totaling 7.15 carat.</p>'=>'<p>一把18K玫瑰金打造的琺瑯折疊扇，飾有雲紋圖案，鑲嵌總重量7.15克拉的圓形鑽石，滿滿優雅情懷。</p>','<p>Inspired by the blue sky and our heritage, Yun Cai, meaning clouds in Chinese, is a collection of fine enamel pieces to celebrate EJI\'s 25th anniversary.</p>'=>'<p>受藍天和傳統文化的啟發，〈雲彩〉是一系列精緻琺瑯作品，慶祝EJI踏入二十五週年。</p>','A COLLECTIVE SENTIMENT'=>'集體情懷','A MODERN TOUCH'=>'詮釋現代風格','A NOD TO OUR HERITAGE'=>'致敬傳統','High Jewellery'=>'高級珠寶','Home'=>'首頁','Yun cai'=>'雲彩','editor-text-editor-0dc733e'=>'<p>受藍天和傳統文化的啟發，〈雲彩〉是一系列精緻琺瑯作品，慶祝EJI踏入二十五週年。</p>','editor-text-editor-a62ff14'=>'<p><span style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; text-align: start;">雲在中國文學中具有情感價值。〈雲彩〉從著名詩人李白和徐志摩的經典詩句裡，尋找靈感。 </span></p>','editor-text-editor-fe8fb2c'=>'<p>一把18K玫瑰金打造的琺瑯折疊扇，飾有雲紋圖案，鑲嵌總重量7.15克拉的圓形鑽石，滿滿優雅情懷。</p>','editor-text-editor-ff29f80'=>'<p>靈感來自折疊扇的流蘇式項鍊。由18K玫瑰金製成，鑲嵌總重量2.34克拉的圓形鑽石，演繹新舊融合之美。 </p>','icon-list-text-90cc29b-23ba1e0'=>'高級珠寶','icon-list-text-90cc29b-24b69d8'=>'首頁','icon-list-url-90cc29b-23ba1e0'=>'https://eji.com.hk/zh-hant/%e9%ab%98%e7%b4%9a%e7%8f%a0%e5%af%b6/'